        %h1 Addiscent Tools
        %p.aligncenter Addiscent has recently begun developing a growing collection of Open Source tools, described below.
        %p  
        %h2 Vagrant-Ruby-Rails
        %p
          %strong Vagrant-Ruby-Rails
          is a tool for Ruby On Rails developers. It is a Vagrant Box,
          = succeed "" do
            %a{:href => "https://www.vagrantup.com"} https://www.vagrantup.com
        %p Because it can be quickly built or rebuilt if necessary, Vagrant-Ruby-Rails may be handy for transient work environments, such as tutorials, or experimental work which may sacrifice the development environment.
        %p It also allows easy reproduction and distribution of exact duplicates of a development environment shared among multiple project members.
        %p
          For more information, read all about it on the
          = succeed "." do
            %a{:href => "https://github.com/addiscent/vagrant-ruby-rails"} Vagrant-Ruby-Rails GitHub Repository
        %p
          Vagrant-Ruby-Rails is Open Source,
          = succeed "." do
            %a{:href => "http://www.apache.org/licenses/"} Apache v2.0 license
        %br/
        %div.ss-box
          %p.aligncenter
            %h4
