        %h2 IP Log To SQL Database
        %p
          %strong IP Log To SQL Database
          is a command line tool, written in PHP, intended for use by a web site host administrator.  It reads an IP log file, (HTTP Access Log), parses fields from each line, and inserts one row of fields for each line into an SQL database table.
        %p
          It is Open Source, GPL v2.0 license.
        %p
          %a{:href => "https://github.com/addiscent/iplog-to-sql-table"} Download it from GitHub
          and use it as is or modify it to suit your purposes.
        %p  
        %div.ss-box
          %p.aligncenter
